ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of PENNY JANE WESTMAN of Westmount, Quebec, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Rafik Souccar, whose term has expired.
